Package: gpbiometrics
Type: Package
Title: Process and Report Gazepoint Biometrics Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Stefanos", family = "Balaskas", email = "s.balaskas@ac.upatras.gr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Imports, validates, quality-checks, preprocesses, summarises, synchronises,
        models, plots, and reports Gazepoint Biometrics exports. The package focuses
        on Gazepoint-specific biometric channels such as GSR/EDA, heart rate,
        interbeat intervals, pulse and PPG signals, engagement dial, TTL markers, and
        synchronisation fields that can be combined with Gazepoint GP3 and GP3 HD
        eye-tracking workflows. It also includes Gazepoint-aware HR/IBI/HRV and
        HeartPy-style pulse/PPG preparation, peak-detection, quality-control, and
        reporting helpers.
